#12
 妄想.救災換WHO會員. 於 2008/05/20 05:40


 


                                剛剛在Bloomberg.com上看到一篇有關四川救災的後續相關報導.這是由William 
Bi,email:wbi@bloomberg.net 及 Eugene Tang, email:eugenetang@bloomberg.net
兩位所發稿的.前臺北市副市長歐晉德率領的救難隊,還有全台的愛心捐款如此巨大.老共就是要讓
台灣肉包子打狗.錢來Ok.人來幫忙,OK.台灣要在國際發聲:免談.大家寫信去Bloomberg給這兩位
抗議一下.以下提供範本copy + paste就可以寄啦.
I'm really frustrated that Taiwan is intentionally ignored to be reported 
even the donation for Sichuan earthquake from Taiwan official government 
is No 1 for any single goverment in the world.  
Taiwan has also sent experienced earthquake experts to help the natural 
disaster.  Why you never mention it?  Doesn't Taiwan deserve some words 
from you?                            

 


 
 

 
 

















